{"ProductId":"30","Title":"Canyon Ridge<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Carriage House (5-Layer)","ShortDescription":"Insulated carriage house garage doors with faux wood composite cladding and overlays","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/cr5l-des11-rec13-tampa-showcase.webp?sfvrsn=d9bffbb6_1","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/canyonridge","Overview":"<div class=\"d-flex mt-3 mt-lg-4\" data-section-id=\"Durable Construction\"><h3>Built to Impress, Engineered to Last</h3></div><div class=\"d-flex mt-3 mt-lg-4\" data-section-id=\"Layer\"><h4>5-Layer Strength</h4></div><p>Durable steel base, high-performance insulation, and another layer of steel, all topped with moisture-resistant composite cladding and overlays for serious staying power.</p><h4>Authentic Wood Appearance</h4><p>Composite materials are molded from real wood boards, capturing the look and feel of premium hardwoods like Clear Cypress or Mahogany without the high maintenance.</p><h4>Customized to Fit Your Style</h4><p>Pick from 15 classic carriage house designs, optional windows, and decorative hardware. Choose from 10 standard paint or stain finishes or get creative with over 1,500 <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg;</a> custom shades.</p><h4>Superior Comfort &amp; Efficiency</h4><p>The 2\" <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg; polyurethane insulation</a> keeps your garage comfortable year-round, with an impressive R-value of 20.4.</p><h4>Tough in Any Weather</h4><p>Optional <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg; reinforcement</a> is available for extra strength in high-wind areas.</p><h4>Environmental Assurance</h4><p>Clopay doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay\r\n    doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<h3>Engineered for Strength and Lasting Beauty</h3><p>The Canyon Ridge&reg; Carriage House (5-Layer) is designed to give you the authentic look of wood and the rugged durability of steel. Each door starts with a heavy-duty steel base, layered with advanced Intellicore&reg; polyurethane insulation for maximum energy efficiency and a quieter garage. On top of that, you&rsquo;ll find another layer of steel for extra strength, then moisture-resistant composite cladding and overlays that capture the rich detail of real wood without the worry of warping, rotting, or splitting.</p><p>All hardware is built to last, with rust-resistant components and reinforced safety brackets for added peace of mind. The door&rsquo;s finish stands up to the elements and needs only occasional cleaning&mdash;no sanding, staining, or painting required. Every detail is designed for low maintenance, long-term performance, and reliable safety, so you can focus on enjoying your home&rsquo;s curb appeal instead of worrying about upkeep.</p><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-canyon-ridge-ch-5l.webp?sfvrsn=ba04eee_5\" alt=\"Canyon Ridge 5-Layer Cutaway\" sf-size=\"100\" /><p>&nbsp;</p><ol><li>Composite Overlay</li><li>Composite Cladding</li><li>Steel</li><li>2\" Intellicore&reg; Polyurethane Insulation</li><li>Steel</li></ol>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"Canyon Ridge Carriage House (5-Layer)","DisplayIndex":3,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/canyon-ridge-5-layer","ColorDisclaimer":"<p>Your Canyon Ridge&reg; Carriage House (5-Layer) door comes in a wide palette of finishes designed to showcase its wood-look beauty. Choose from timeless stains like Natural, Medium, Dark, Walnut, Slate, or Espresso for a classic, elegant appearance that highlights the grain and texture of the faux wood.</p><p>For something bolder with a contemporary edge, select models are available in Black, White, Bronze, or Charcoal. These colors are exclusive to Mahogany overlays, adding depth and drama to your garage.</p><p>For even more personality, try the two-tone option: pick one color for the steel base and another for the composite overlay to create a truly custom look. And if you have a specific shade in mind, the Color Blast&reg; program offers over 1,500 custom colors, so your door can perfectly match your home.</p><p><em>*Available on select models.<br />Black, white, bronze and charcoal only available in Mahogany.<br />Two-tone option available. One color for the base layer (steel) and one color for the top layer (composite overlay).<br /></em></p>","TopSectionDisclaimer":"<p>Canyon Ridge&reg; Carriage House (5-Layer) doors offer a wide range of window and top section options, so you can tailor the look to your style. Prefer a simple, solid top for a sleek finish? Choose from several solid panel designs, including traditional rectangular and graceful arched shapes.</p><p>If you want to add natural light and character, there&rsquo;s a whole lineup of window configurations including rectangular, square, and arch-topped styles, with or without decorative grilles. For double doors, special double-arched and wide window arrangements create a balanced, eye-catching appearance.</p>","HardwareDisclaimer":"<p>Every Canyon Ridge® Carriage House (5-Layer) door comes with spade lift handles as standard, bringing a hint of classic carriage house charm. Want to personalize your look? There’s a full collection of optional hardware, including spear and colonial lift handles, decorative styles, and even ring door knockers for a truly vintage vibe.</p>\r\n<p>Step plates and strap hinges are available in matching spade, spear, or colonial shapes, letting you coordinate every detail. All hardware pieces are crafted from weather-resistant materials and finished in classic black, so they stand up to the elements while adding bold contrast and character.</p>\r\n","DesignDisclaimer":"","RelatedProducts":[{"Title":"Canyon Ridge<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Carriage House (4-Layer)","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/cr4l-d21-rec13-afp143r.webp?sfvrsn=8ae1d536_3","Id":"29","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/canyon-ridge-4-layer","DisplayIndex":4,"ShortDescription":"Stylish, low maintenance and insulated faux wood garage doors","AlternativeText":"Canyon Ridge Carriage House (4-Layer)"},{"Title":"Gallery<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Steel","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/gallery-steel-ug-long-rec14-595.webp?sfvrsn=a7ceae04_9","Id":"12","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/gallerysteel","DisplayIndex":8,"ShortDescription":"Grooved panel steel carriage house garage doors","AlternativeText":"Gallery Steel"},{"Title":"Coachman<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup>","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/coachman-d21-rec13-davidson-595.webp?sfvrsn=d3817fcc_10","Id":"11","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/coachman","DisplayIndex":12,"ShortDescription":"The perfect blend of beauty and practicality, these doors are crafted of durable steel and insulation topped with a textured composite overlay","AlternativeText":"Coachman"},{"Title":"Grand Harbor<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup>","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/grand-harbor-schanen-595.webp?sfvrsn=91e18ec0_2","Id":"27","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/grandharbor","DisplayIndex":13,"ShortDescription":"When budget i